@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #ECEFF1
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBorderColor #455A64
skinparam shadowing true
[*] --> Reviewed
Reviewed --> Archived : cancel
Archived --> Approved : reject
Approved --> Pending : process
Pending --> Completed : cancel
Pending : entry / log checkout
Completed --> Cancelled : approve
Completed : entry / log checkout
Cancelled --> Reviewed : revert
Cancelled --> [*]
@enduml